    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-7-2025-07_32_26-PM.png" alt="HECM for Purchase: Buy Your Retirement Home Without Monthly Payments" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
